Hello, thank you for calling Harmonious Sounds Music School. My name is Russell Sanchez. May I have your name, please?

Hi, Russell. My name is Frances Jackson.

Nice to meet you, Frances. How can I assist you today?

Well, I'm a bit disappointed with the quality of the violin lessons. I expected more based on the reviews.

I'm sorry to hear that you're disappointed, Frances. Could you please provide more specifics on what aspects of the lessons you're unhappy with?

The instructor seems a bit unprepared, and I haven’t noticed any improvement in my technique over the past few weeks.

Thank you for sharing that with me. To better address this issue, may I ask for your enrollment ID, Frances?

Sure, it's FJ-one zero three two.

And could you also confirm your email address for our records?

Of course. It's frances.jackson at email dot com.

Thank you for your patience, Frances. I'll make sure this feedback is passed on to the right department so we can improve your experience. We really appreciate your input.

Thank you, Russell. I hope things improve soon.

You're welcome, Frances. Thank you for bringing this to our attention. Have a great day!
